	<dl>
	<dt>i do not endorse the existence of the...</dt>
	<dd><p>i do not endorse the existence of the state and find it deaming that i am expected to consent to others having power and control over me.  i am certainly not ignorant of the powers and systems that govern us and do much in the way of protest, boycots and direct action to overthrow them.  struggle against systems of authority is the natural  reaction of every individual striving for their freedom.  if we all took responsiblity for our own lives and impact on the planet the world would be a much better place.</p>
	<small>
	written 4th May 2005 <!--  | <a href="../email/1680">Email this
    to a friend</a> | <a
    href="/abuse/?postid=1680">abusive?</a> -->
	</small>
	</dd>
	</dl>

