	<p><em><strong>Boojam</strong> replies:</em> If the state didn't exist, there would still be people with control and power over you, and they wouldn't in any way be accountable to you, just the most aggressive and unpleasant individuals clawing their way to the top of the heap. This is what happens in countries without vaguely well-functioning states.</p>
	<small>
	written 4th May 2005 <!-- | <a
